Chapter 12 - John&rsquo;s Rise and the Questioner&rsquo;s Change#At Katherine&rsquo;s shack, a member of Richard&rsquo;s group, John stared at the maps. &ldquo;Gosh, it&rsquo;s been so long, Katherine, so that&rsquo;s where you were going.&rdquo;
